(6071, 1, '2016-12-12 21:59:30', '2016-12-12 20:59:30', 'http://vimeo.com/100858912\n\nGot the opportunity to travel to Sochi Russia for Royale and hang out with a bunch of Olympians(!) to install an interactive social media video wall in the athlete villages for Cole & Weber United and the International Olympic Committee at the 2014 Olympic Games. \nIt pulled realtime inspirational messages and images from social media sites across all nations (like not just Twitter Facebook but also  and ) and stitched them into an endlessly parallax scrolling mosaic of support for the athletes.  \nAdditionally, produced the mobile site for the athletes to navigate their Sochi experience. It was developed as an Android app which was preloaded onto everyone\'s brand new Galaxy Note 3\'s as a gift from Olympic sponsor Samsung, or as a mobile web app for the athletes who were stuck on their old phones. The above custom character video animation welcomed the teams to the next 17 days of Olympic history. \n\nMore info on Royale\'s site at <a href="http://weareroyale.com/#/work/all/athlete-interactive-engagement/" title="IOC Sochi Athlete Experientals">http://weareroyale.com/#/work/all/athlete-interactive-engagement/</a>', 'IOC Welcome to Sochi', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6068-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-12-12 21:59:30', '2016-12-12 20:59:30', '', 6068, 'http://localhost/6068-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
